nodes.title: Positive Prompt
widgets_values: A photo-realistic shoot from a front camera angle about a woman sitting on a wooden bench in an outdoor setting, wearing traditional clothing and jewelry. the image also shows a candle on a candlestand in the foreground. on the middle of the image, a woman with long, wavy, dark brown hair appears to be in her early twenties, sitting with her legs crossed. she is wearing a maroon kimono with intricate gold embroidery and a beige top underneath. she has a serious expression on her face and is looking directly at the camera. her hair is adorned with colorful earrings and jewelry, including a necklace, bracelets, and earrings. her feet are bare and she has toenails. the background is an old, rustic building with a dark door and a wooden door frame, and the lighting is soft and warm, casting gentle shadows.
